					.title Consultant General &amp; Colorectal Surgeon
					.place Epsom and St Helier NHS Trust
					%p Recently appointed Consultant in St Helier, he has been involved in Colorectal surgery for some time. His particular interests and experienc lie in laparoscopic gastrointestinal and colorectal surgery, colorectal cancer, screening and colonscopy.

				%section
					.lecturer Jan Walker and Julia Russell
					.title Respiratory Nurse Specialists
					.place Epsom and St Helier NHS Trust
					%p The aim of the respiratory nursing service is to support patients with lung disease in the community and to be a source of advice to members of the multidisciplinary team. We aim to reduce admission rates for COPD by ensuring correct diagnosis and management and early intervention for exacerbations.

				%section
					.lecturer Sandeep H Cliff
					.title Consultant Dermatologist and Dermsurgeon
					.place Epsom and St Helier NHS Trust
					%p His area of interest is the surgical management of dermatological conditions which includes skin cancer as well as non cancerous conditions such as hyperhidrosis and penile dermatosis. His research interests are clinical and include the psychological affect of dermatological conditions on patients. He has in addition, over the passed year lectured internationally on skin cancer and its management.
